* steps to set up something with react + flux

*. npm init
*. npm install webpack react react-dom flux classnames immutable --save
*. npm install babel-loader babel-core babel-preset-env babel-preset-react --save-dev
*. webpack.config.js
*. package.json (optional) add build, watch
*. dir structure (e.g. js/, css/, src/ etc)
*. index.html, base.css, root.js
*. add some stuff to root.js and run webpack (webpack/npm run build)
